    List&lt;Element&gt; arraylist = Arrays.&lt;Element&gt;asList(array);

Another simple way is to add all elements from the array to a new ArrayList using a for-each loop.

    ArrayList&lt;Element&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();

	for(Element e : array)
