         public static &lt;T&gt; List&lt;T&gt; asList(T... a) //varargs are of T type. 

   So, you might initialize `arraylist` like this: 

         List&lt;Element&gt; arraylist = Arrays.asList(new Element(1), new Element(2), new Element(3));

